@startuml
hide footbox
skinparam linetype ortho

actor Client as 客户端
participant Controller as ActivityPlanController
participant Service as ActivityPlanService
participant DB as 数据库

== 新增活动方案 ==

客户端 -> Controller : POST /api/activity-plans\n（方案 + 内容 + 步骤）
Controller -> Controller : 参数校验\n（必填 / stepNumber / season掩码）

Controller -> Service : createActivityPlan(dto)

activate Service
Service -> DB : BEGIN TRANSACTION

Service -> DB : INSERT activity_plan\n返回 planId
note right of DB
生成主键 planId
作为聚合根ID
end note

Service -> DB : INSERT activity_plan_content\n(activity_plan_id = planId)
note right of DB
1:1 表\nUNIQUE(activity_plan_id)
end note

Service -> DB : BATCH INSERT activity_step\n(activity_plan_id = planId)
note right of DB
1:N 表\n(step_number 唯一)
end note

Service -> DB : COMMIT

deactivate Service

Service --> Controller : 创建成功
Controller --> 客户端 : 200 OK / planId

== 异常情况 ==

Service -> DB : ROLLBACK
note right of Service
任一步失败：
- 外键失败
- 唯一约束
- 业务校验异常
end note

Controller --> 客户端 : 4xx / 5xx 错误信息

@enduml
